    <item>
      <title>Snowboarding in Oslo</title>
      <link>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2011/03/06/snowboarding-in-oslo/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Mar 2011 22:40:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2011/03/06/snowboarding-in-oslo/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m snowboarding in Oslo for three days and I can say it is a lovely place. The scenery is amazing and the snow is awesome too. The air is a special Nordic fresh that fills your lungs with goodness each time you take a breath.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
